page.title: 20FISHLAKE SHOW
page.content: AN ANNUAL SHOW BASED ON THE LINES OF AN OLD AGRICULTURAL SHOW FOR THE FISHLAKE AREA. IT IS HELD IN A FIELD JUST OUTSIDE THE VILLAGE OF FISH SHEEP, COWS AND GOATS ARE SHOWN AND SOLD.THERE IS SHOW JUMPING WITH EVENTS FOR YOUNG RIDERS. THERE ARE TENTS CONTAINING EXHIBITIONS OF FLOWER ARRANGING, PAINTINGS BY LOCAL ARTISTS AND BAKING. THERE IS A DOG SHOW FOR PET DOGS AND ROSETTES AND CASH PRIZES ARE AWARDED TO WINNERS.IN RECENT YEARS INVITED VISITORS HAVE BROUGHT COLLECTIONS OF DIFFERENT ANIMALS TO SHOW. SOME OF THE INTERESTING SPECIES WE HAVE SEEN HAVE BEEN SNAKES, BIRDS OF PREY AND UNUSUAL FISH. DOMESDAY PROJECT INFORMATION COLLECTED BY THE CHILDREN OF FISHLAKE ENDOWED FIRST SCHOOL.
